Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Brand-new, 15-year absolute NNN single-tenant ground-lease investment opportunity (15 years remaining).
Excellent 2.00% annual increases throughout the initial 15-year lease term and throughout Swig’s three (3), five-year renewal option periods.
Brand-new construction featuring Swig’s new prototype design (Delivering in October 2021).
Savory currently operates 65 locations across 5 brands including: Swig, Via313 Pizzeria, R&R Barbeque, Mo’ Bettah - Hawaiian Style and The Crack Shack.
The Property is well-located in the Oklahoma City metropolitan area, approximately 8 miles southeast from OKC’s downtown booming corridor, in Midwest City, Oklahoma.

The Property is located just north of Town Center Plaza, a prominent power center which features major national retailers such as: Dick’s Sporting Goods, Lowe’s, Target, Best Buy, Kohl’s, PetSmart, Office Depot, Marshalls, JC Penney, Raising Cane’s, Steak n’ Shake, Pei Wei and Blaze Pizza, among many others.
Zero Landlord responsibility coupled with a stable, long-term income stream – well positioned for 1031 exchange investors.
In 2019, Money.com named Midwest City one of the Top 100 Places to Live in the United States.
Over 23,500 vehicles per day along Air Depot Boulevard, a major north south commuter thoroughfare (Association of Central Oklahoma Governments 2020)
Strong density of 68,846 residents in a three-mile radius and 121,072 residents in a five-mile radius (Source: Claritas).

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: This brand-new Swig is well-positioned on the northeast corner of Douglas Drive and Air Depot Boulevard at 2590 South Air Depot Boulevard in Midwest City, Oklahoma, approximately 8 miles southeast from Oklahoma City’s downtown corridor. The Property features excellent monument signage and visibility along Air Depot Boulevard, a major north-south commuter thoroughfare which yields ±23,500 vehicles per day*. The Property is located in a large commercial trade area and positioned just north of Town Center Plaza which features major national retail brands such as: Lowe’s, Target, Dick’s Sporting Goods, PetSmart, Kohl’s, Best Buy, Marshalls, Ulta Beauty, Raising Cane’s, Chili’s, Blaze Pizza, Verizon, Jack in the Box, Chick-Fil-A, Steak N’ Shake and Lane Bryant, among many others. (Source: Association of Central Oklahoma Governments 2020)

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to offer for sale this brand-new, single-tenant, absolute-NNN ground lease with Swig-N-Sweets (the “Property) located at 2590 South Air Depot Boulevard in Midwest City, Oklahoma, approximately 8 miles southeast from Oklahoma City’s downtown corridor. The Property is well-positioned on the northeast corner of Douglas Drive and Air Depot Boulevard in a highly trafficked commercial trade area of Midwest City, just north of Town Center Plaza which features Target, Lowe’s Home Improvement and Dick’s Sporting Goods, among many others. The offering consists of a 100% leased, absolute NNN ground lease with Swig, which is under construction and expected to deliver in October 2021. Rent commencement will begin at the close of escrow which includes a brand-new 15-year, absolute-NNN ground lease with Swig. The lease features 2% annual rental increases in the initial term and throughout the tenant’s three (3), five-year renewal option periods.
